    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are recorded as not-assessed, which is acceptable per the ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 scoping rules. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the candidate CPB device hemolysis performance is non-inferior to the predicate (RH < 1.0 at all operating points). The assessment team concludes the model is fit for the stated COU.",
